<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="page" lang="ru">
    <head>
        {{ include('include/head.html.twig') }}
        <title>{% block title %}{{ land.name }}{% endblock %}</title>
    </head>
    <body onload="InitPageTheme()">
        {{ include('include/nav.html.twig') }}
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <div class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissible fade show mt-4" role="alert">
                                <span class="alert-text"><strong>Внимание!</strong> Данные о городах обновляются каждые 15-30 минут.</span>
                                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
                                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 mt-4">
                            <div class="block lands">
                                <div class="block-header block-header-lands">
                                    <div class="block-title d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <p class="lands-circle"></p>
                                        <p class="lands-title">#{{ land.id }} — {{ land.name }}</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="block-body block-body-lands block-border-top">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 block-text lands-text">
                                            <p><strong>Количество жителей в городе:</strong> {{ land.membersQuantity }}</p>
                                            <p><strong>Координаты расположения:</strong> {{ land.location.x|round }}, {{ land.location.y|round }}, {{ land.location.z|round }}</p>
                                            <p><strong>Баланс казны города:</strong> {{ land.balance }} золотых монет</p>
                                            <p><strong>Дата создания города:</strong> {{ land.createdAt }}</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-12 mt-3 col-lg-4 mt-lg-0 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                                            <div class="block">
                                                <div class="block-header block-radius">
                                                    <img class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center m-auto" width="32" style="border-radius: 4px" alt="" src="https://mc-cloudy.com/public/images/playerhead.png">
                                                    <p class="block-title text-center mt-2 mb-0" style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -.1px; line-height: 1">{{ land.owner }}</p>
                                                    <p class="block-title mt-0 mb-0" style="text-transform: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -.1px; line-height: 1">Правитель города</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-none d-lg-block col-12 col-lg-4">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-12">
                            {{ include('include/social-links.html.twig') }}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{ include('include/footer.html.twig') }}
        </div>
    </body>
</html>